<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0,width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,date=no,address=no">
    <title>文档</title>
     <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/api.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/aui.2.0.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/style.css"/>
     <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/swiper.min.css" />
     <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/iconfont.css" />
    <style>
       html,body{
        background: #F5F5F5;
      }
      .aui-list:before{
		  height:0px;
		}
		.btn-box{
		  width:100%;
		  background: #fff;
		  height: 50px;
		  text-align: center;
		  padding-top: 10px;
		}
		.btn-box .aui-btn{
		  width: 95%;
		  padding: 5px;
		  font-size: 1rem;
		}
		.fix-box{
		  position: fixed;
		  bottom:0px;
		}
    /*列表*/     
    .purple{
       color: #bf6cef;   
    }
      .youquan-list-box{
             display: -webkit-box;
			display: -webkit-flex;
			display: flex;
			-webkit-flex-flow: row;
			flex-flow: row;
			background: #fff url("../../image/bg-ico.jpg") no-repeat right top;
			background-size:16px;
			font-size: 0.875rem;
			height: 120px;	
			border-radius: 5px;	
			margin-bottom: 10px;
      }     
       .list-left-all{
            -webkit-box-flex: 1;
			-webkit-flex: 1;
			flex: 1;
      }
      .list-right-all{
           width: 6rem;
           border-left:1px dashed #ddd;
           padding: 0px 5px 0px 5px;
      }
      .list-right-all span{
        text-align: center;
        display: block;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }
      
      .list-left-top{
          height: 40px;
          padding: 2px 0px 7px 10px;
          color:#000;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .list-left-top img{
        width: 35px;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 5px;
        
      }
      .list-left-bottom{
        padding: 6px 0px 4px 10px; 
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .list-left-bottom img{
        width: 100px;
         float: left;
      }
      .card1 .use-btn{
        border:1px solid #6612fb;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #bf6cef;
        color:#fff;
        padding: 3px 0px 3px 0px;
      }
      .card1 .much-box{
        float: left;
        margin-left: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .card1 .much-box b{
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #bf6cef;
      }     
       /*列表*/
      
      /*详情*/
     .content-all{
			  overflow: hidden;
			  padding-bottom: 50px;
			}
     .tel-img{
			 width: 35px;
			}
			.word-box{
			  background: #fff;
			  margin-top:10px;
			  padding: 10px;
			}
			.word-box h1{
			  font-size: 0.875rem;
			  padding-bottom: 5px;
			  margin-bottom: 5px;
			}
			.word-box p{
			   line-height: 18px;
			}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="content-all">
<div class="aui-content-padded">
  <div class="youquan-list-box card1" >
      <div class="list-left-all " onclick="youquanContent()">
       <div class="list-left-top">
         <img src="../../image/logo-icon01.png">延长<b class="red">e</b>加油平台团购券
       </div>
       <div class="list-left-bottom">
         <img src="../../image/card5.jpg">
         <div class="much-box"> 
                                                 剩余：<br>
            <b>￥1000.00</b>                             
         </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="list-right-all">
      <span class="aui-font-size-14 purple">92#汽油</span>
      <span class="aui-font-size-14 purple">5000元</span>
        <span class="aui-font-size-14">有效日期截止</span>
        <span class="aui-font-size-14">2016.12.31</span>
        <span onclick="zhifubox()" class="use-btn">去使用</span>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>

<ul class="aui-list aui-margin-t-15">
        <li class="aui-list-item aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
            <div class="aui-list-item-inner">
                <div class="aui-list-item-title ">适用油站 （离我最近）</div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="aui-list-item aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
            <div class="aui-list-item-inner">
                <div class="aui-list-item-title">曲江庙坡头油站     30.00km<br><span style="color: #888">近西安唐城墙遗址公园</span></div>
                <div class="aui-list-item-right"><img class="tel-img" src="../../image/tel-ico1.jpg"></div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="aui-list-item aui-list-item-arrow aui-padded-t-10 aui-padded-b-10">
            <div class="aui-list-item-inner">
                <div class="aui-list-item-title">全部门店信息</div>
                <div class="aui-list-item-right aui-font-size-16">共24站</div>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="word-box">
     <h1 class="aui-border-b">团购细则</h1>
     <p>1.有效期: 自购买日起12月内有效</p>
<p>2.该团购券限延长加油合作站使用</p>
<p>3.无需预约、不可退款、不设找零，可分次消费</p>
<p>4.不允许散装买油</p>
<p>5.团购券与优惠券不可叠加使用且优先使用团购券</p>
<p>6.请根据可用油站选择购买</p>
    </div>
</div>    
</div>    
    <div class="btn-box fix-box">
     <div class="aui-btn aui-btn-danger" onclick="zhuanzeng()">转赠朋友</div>
    </div>
    
</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/aui-tab.js" ></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/jquery.min.js" ></script>
<script>
  
  //展开油站详情
    $("#chakanList").click(function(){
      $(".youzhan-content").toggleClass("displayNone")
    })
  
  //打开转增
  function zhuanzeng(){
    api.openWin({
	    name: 'my-zhuanzeng-head',
	    url: 'my-zhuanzeng-head.html'
    });    
  }
</script>
</html>